      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable, stylish ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been so well-loved and is still looking fantastic! It runs like a dream and is perfect for everything from your daily commute to those fun weekend road trips. It's super comfortable and has plenty of life left in it. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels on the road!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
