      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This example features the 3.6L flat-six M96 engine paired with a 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance is documented, including a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The chassis remains taut with an upgraded M030-spec suspension and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers gripping cross-drilled rotors. While the Arctic Silver paint shows minor road patina, the engine exhibits no bore scoring and the DME report shows zero overrevs in higher ranges. A high-performance driver's spec ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips from highway driving that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are plush and intact, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has a documented service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a responsive engine that feels as strong as the day it was built. It sits on a set of high-tread tires and needs nothing but a new driver. If you are looking for a reliable, sharp-looking daily driver that bridges the gap between 'used' and 'new,' this is the ideal candidate.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a clean interior and a robust powertrain, it represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable high-caliber vehicle. Contact our sales department to arrange a viewing.",
      "price": 32500.0,
