      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes. The interior is nice and tidy, and it still drives like a dream! It\u2019s the perfect fit for someone looking for a reliable, well-cared-for vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take a look\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This A80 chassis maintains its sequential twin-turbocharged configuration, delivering linear boost across the rev range. Mated to the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen LSD, the drivetrain remains tight with crisp gear engagement. The suspension geometry is intact, utilizing the original double-wishbone setup for predictable cornering dynamics. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-quality status, the structural integrity and forced induction system have been fastidiously maintained. A perfect candidate for the purist seeking a solid mechanical foundation.",
      "price": 32500.0,
